relation: Holy. I'd forgotten that I'd made it this far on this picture. It still isn't finished, but it never will be, seeing that I haven't touched it for over three years, so here it is.
One of the sentry robots employed by Pokey in the Monotoli Building. Another unfinished image, but I haven't worked on it in years and always liked how it was progressing.
The Dragon from Mother 1, finally awake. I was so close to completing this before, but never could bring myself to put the finishing touches on it, so here it is.

A Putird Moldy man sketch that i made for one of teh Fangamer packing slips. I love it dearly because it STARTED as a sketch of an Insane Cultist, but I felt I botched it, and managed to turn the lines I'd already made into this drawing -- had that mistake never occurred, I'd have never made this drawing. And this drawing makes me happy. :)
A commissioned painting of the good Dr. Andonuts. Acrylics on 9"x12" canvas board.
